You’re done!

30
00:04:11,300 --> 00:04:12,860
Congratulations!

31
00:04:13,820 --> 00:04:21,940
By the way, did you know that the /ə/ sound is written as the letter “a” in one-third of all cases?

32
00:04:22,620 --> 00:04:24,780
More on the spelling:

33
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:32,280
Most often, the /ə/ sound is written as the letter “a,” as in the word “above,”

34
00:04:32,540 --> 00:04:36,040
then by the letter “o,” as in the word “today,”

35
00:04:36,340 --> 00:04:39,360
and the letter “e,” as in the word “even.”

36
00:04:39,980 --> 00:04:45,860
Less often it’s represented by a combination of the letters “io,” as in the word “nation”;

37
00:04:45,860 --> 00:04:48,540
the letter “i,” as in the word “pencil”,

38
00:04:48,540 --> 00:04:51,520
and the letter “u,” as in the word “product.”

